   version stable 1.0.2 0.0.24
   require pkgconfig shishi
      opts --disable-static
  category security/encryption
 attribute library makej multilib-concurrent
    source $GNU_URL gss/gss-$VERSION.tar.gz
#   source ftp://alpha.gnu.org/gnu/gss/gss-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info last 20111125
      info home http://www.gnu.org/software/gss/
      info docs http://www.gnu.org/software/gss/manual/gss.html
      desc 'implementation of the generic security service API
gss is Generic Security Service is an implementation
of the Generic Security Service API (GSSAPI).
It is used by network applications to provide security services,
such as authenticating SMTP/IMAP, via the GSSAPI SASL mechanism.
It consists of a library and a manual, and a Kerberos 5 mechanism
that supports mutual authentication and the DES and 3DES ciphers.'
